# =============================================================================
# SQL Server MCP Environment Variables Configuration
# =============================================================================
# 
# üìñ COMPLETE DOCUMENTATION: See docs/ENV-VARS.md for detailed information
#    about all environment variables, defaults, and context-aware behavior.
#
